# Whitelist build context for the API image (see Dockerfile header).
# Everything is excluded, then ONLY what the Dockerfile COPYs is re-included —
# a local working tree carries multi-GB untracked artefacts (data/bronze 7GB+,
# raw Iris/SIPO/CRO pulls) that must never reach the docker daemon.

*

# build inputs
!pyproject.toml
!uv.lock
!paths.py
!config.py

# code + the SQL view firewall
!api/
!dail_tracker_core/
!sql_views/

# data: ONLY the directories the registered views read (kept in sync with
# `grep -rhoE "data/[A-Za-z0-9_./-]+" sql_views/`). data/bronze and raw pull
# dirs stay out; runtime-generated export snapshots are rebuilt in-container.
!data/gold/parquet/
!data/_meta/
!data/silver/parquet/
!data/silver/charities/
!data/silver/committees/
!data/silver/cro/
!data/silver/lobbying/parquet/
!data/silver/lobbying/client_company_returns_detail.csv
!data/silver/aggregated_td_tables.csv
!data/silver/seanad_aggregated_tables.csv
!data/silver/flattened_members.csv
!data/silver/flattened_seanad_members.csv
!data/silver/ministerial_tenure.parquet

# big untracked artefacts that live inside whitelisted dirs
data/gold/parquet/speeches_fact_full.parquet
data/_export_cache/
**/__pycache__/
